text: @BorisJohnson @BorisJohnson The most recent newsworthy export from the UK to New Zealand was COVID-19. Successfully exported via two New Zealanders who flew there from the UK. That took NZ’s cases from zero to two. #coronavirus #NewZealand #uk #export
